metadata.documentation: Comprehend Medical extracts structured information from unstructured clinical text. Use these actions to gain insight in your documents.

DetectEntities.documentation: Inspects the clinical text for a variety of medical entities and returns specific information about them such as entity category, location, and confidence score on that information .

exceptions.documentation: An internal server error occurred. Retry your request.

DetectPHI.documentation: Inspects the clinical text for personal health information (PHI) entities and entity category, location, and confidence score on that information.

Attribute.documentation: An extracted segment of the text that is an attribute of an entity, or otherwise related to an entity, such as the dosage of a medication taken. It contains information about the attribute such as id, begin and end offset within the input text, and the segment of the input text.
